{"tid":1372371,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"撤退決定係由前線傳去後面, not the other way around","createTime":"2019-07-27T12:03:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T08:30:19.000Z","uid":1988,"like":70,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"04d88e08ff95203083f0aa1e6b490e8fa6d0bc81","tid":1372371,"uid":1988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T12:03:24.000Z","msg":"我再講多一次<br />\n你企後邊 你做冷氣軍師<br />\n收到風會俾人圍<br />\n你應該將呢個訊息傳去前邊<br />\n而唔係自擺自為叫後面撤退<br />\n<br />\n下下出嚟搞亂軍心 做豬隊友 仲賤過鬼"},{"pid":"ffabcfcea078533a139857568a6f8ffe6d2e6bbf","tid":1372371,"uid":1988,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T12:09:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n麻煩大家搞清楚自己角色<br />\n<br />\n你鍾意出謀獻策冇問題<br />\n不過決定只能夠由前線做"},{"pid":"2b759b745077d17c3dfd1fd093d2f42d3fdda414","tid":1372371,"uid":1988,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T12:14:18.000Z","msg":"再講 今次運動係冇大台冇領袖<br />\n<br />\n咁樣嘅方式 注定咗我地呢一方冇辦法用到一d 好細緻 需要協調嘅打法<br />\n<br />\n我地只能打士氣波 團結波<br />\n<br />\n你喺後面叫散水<br />\n搞亂軍心<br />\n即係等同摧毀我地勝利嘅可能"},{"pid":"0e6d7b56e8d708aa6a2b936e4191dc419fb9f9f8","tid":1372371,"uid":1988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T12:19:34.000Z","msg":"喂喂 睇完麻煩幫手推推<br />\n我好攰 想抖抖"},{"pid":"dd7e456667188d09b09e804a8adb3381c4b72d78","tid":1372371,"uid":79046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T12:21:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f46349767eef42655e09e68bb8e50ce5443968d2","tid":1372371,"uid":1988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T12:33:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed008d105fb3636dab8748cb7b4ba6a3e8ecb37a","tid":1372371,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T12:33:27.000Z","msg":"有無人知白衫去向？"},{"pid":"a90a50e343e010bc96b31aa0d727740913e2c508","tid":1372371,"uid":1988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy